joinMessages: Whoa, whoa, whoa, when did ${user} get here?

854967146244997140.description: Staff will be here soon! Be patient, check back in a few hours. While you're waiting, give some details about your server and maybe a few screenshots. Read the announcements for some conditions.

855588971455578112.description: When you're finished the challenge, ping a staff member so they can check. Don't forget to include screenshots and source code!

857632770565865483.description: Thanks for doing this challenge! Send your code and staff will be here soon.

commands.name: createticket
commands.description: Create a ticket message in specified channel with specified description

options.name: channel
options.description: The channel you want to send the ticket message to

options.name: message
options.description: The message you want to send to the channel

options.name: description
options.description: The description of the ticket (is sent when ticket is created)

commands.name: reactionrole
commands.description: Base command for reaction role management

options.name: create
options.description: Create a reaction role message in a specified channel with a specific emote

options.name: channel
options.description: The desired channel to send the message to

options.name: message
options.description: The reaction role message to send

options.name: emote
options.description: The tag of an emote (i.e. '857360464329572363' or 'Skripthut' for Skripthut, or 'ðŸ“°' for newspaper)

options.name: role
options.description: The role you want the reaction role message to have

options.name: add
options.description: Add a role and reaction to a reaction role message

options.name: message
options.description: The message URL of the reaction role message

options.name: emote
options.description: The tag of an emote (i.e. '857360464329572363' or 'Skripthut' for Skripthut, or 'ðŸ“°' for newspaper)

options.name: role
options.description: The role you want to add to the reaction role message

options.name: remove
options.description: Remove a role from a reaction role message

options.name: message
options.description: The message URL of the reaction role message

options.name: role
options.description: The role you want to remove from the reaction role message

commands.name: role
commands.description: Obtain information about all/specific roles, or manage the roles of a member

options.name: roles
options.description: List all the guild's roles

options.name: role
options.description: List all the details of the specified role

options.name: grant
options.description: Give a role to the member

options.name: member
options.description: The member whom you want to add the role to

options.name: role
options.description: The role you want to give to the member

options.name: reason
options.description: The reason why you granted this role (defaults to "Granted by [Your Tag]")

options.name: revoke
options.description: Remove a role from the member

options.name: member
options.description: The member whom you want to remove the role from

options.name: role
options.description: The role you want to remove from the member

options.name: reason
options.description: The reason why you removed this role (defaults to "Removed by [Your Tag]")

commands.name: colourrole
commands.description: Base command for colour role management

options.name: create
options.description: Create a colour role with a chosen HEX code

options.name: colour
options.description: Your chosen colour's HEX code

options.name: remove
options.description: Remove your current colour role
